<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870522-0046 </DOCNO><HL> Markets, Many CompaniesWill Be Closed on Monday---A Wall Street Journal News Roundup</HL><DD> 05/22/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><TEXT>   Stock exchanges, commodities markets, banks and many businesses will be closed throughout the U.S. Monday in observance of Memorial Day. Most federal, state and local government offices will be closed, and there won't be regular mail delivery. </TEXT></DOC>